          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/133/1524613/VO_71_Lyleth_Lunastre_09_F.ogg",
          "text": "I told Aluriel you would come to rescue me and she merely laughed. Well who is laughing now?",
          "status": "pending",
